tip_battle.title: Liquid Flame (Savage)
tip_battle.message:
• ・Uses strong fire attacks.
  • ・Uses attacks that inflict Paralyze, Sap, and weaken resistance to fire.
  • ・Savage Liquid Flame has three forms - human, hand, and tornado - and it changes form when it is dealt a set amount of damage.
  • ・When in human form, it counters with Blaze.
  • ・When in hand form, it counters with Fira.
